{"type":"text","timestamp":1775830137313,"sessionID":"ses_28847e91dffeKYEnxDt5ztXpkt","part":{"id":"prt_d77b926b6001tHoFXUPcVzkk2p","messageID":"msg_d77b8e406001t8Y2TDZZGwVYie","sessionID":"ses_28847e91dffeKYEnxDt5ztXpkt","type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me compile the verification report.\n\n---\n\n## Spec Verification Report: AR-010 — client-go library\n\n### Overall: ❌ NOT COMPLIANT — Major gaps vs spec\n\nThe implementation is an in-memory mock/stub, not a proper Kubernetes client-go library. Many spec-required types, methods, and constructors are missing. No tests exist for the client-go package.\n\n---\n\n### 1. Clientset `Interface`\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` | ❌ Missing | `clientset.go:7-9` only has `RuntimeV1alpha1()` |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` | ✅ Present | `clientset.go:8` |\n\n### 2. `Clientset` struct\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` | ❌ Missing | No `Clientset` struct exists anywhere |\n| Holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | ❌ Missing | Only `FakeClientset` exists in `fake.go` |\n\n### 3. Constructors\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` | ❌ Missing | |\n| `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)` | ❌ Missing | |\n| `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset` | ❌ Missing | |\n| `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset` | ❌ Missing | |\n\n### 4. `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `RESTClient() rest.Interface` | ❌ Missing | `interfaces.go:34-37` lacks this method |\n| `AgentRuntimesGetter` (embedded) | ⚠️ Partial | Methods exist but not as embedded interface |\n| `CodeInterpretersGetter` (embedded) | ⚠️ Partial | Methods exist but not as embedded interface |\n\n### 5. `AgentRuntimeInterface`\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch` | ✅ Present | `interfaces.go:12-21`, `client.go:127-182` |\n| `DeleteCollection(ctx, opts, listOpts) error` | ❌ Missing | Not in interface or implementation |\n| `AgentRuntimeExpansion` (embedded) | ❌ Missing | No expansion interface defined |\n| REST resource plural: `agentruntimes` | ✅ Present | `client.go:11` |\n\n### 6. `CodeInterpreterInterface`\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| CRUD methods (same shape as AgentRuntime) | ✅ Present | `interfaces.go:23-32`, `client.go:193-248` |\n| `DeleteCollection` | ❌ Missing | |\n| `CodeInterpreterExpansion` (embedded) | ❌ Missing | |\n| REST resource plural: `codeinterpreters` | ✅ Present | `client.go:17` |\n\n### 7. REST Configuration\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `GroupVersion` = `SchemeGroupVersion` | ⚠️ Partial | Used in GVR vars but no REST client setup |\n| `APIPath` = `/apis` | ❌ Missing | No REST client exists |\n| Negotiated serializer from scheme | ❌ Missing | No `scheme` package exists |\n\n### 8. Expansion hooks\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `AgentRuntimeExpansion` | ❌ Missing | Not defined anywhere |\n| `CodeInterpreterExpansion` | ❌ Missing | Not defined anywhere |\n\n### 9. Tests\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| client-go tests | ❌ Missing | No `*_test.go` files in `client-go/` |\n\n### 10. Module path\n\n| Requirement | Status | Detail |\n|---|---|---|\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | ✅ Present | All imports match |\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Deficiencies\n\n**Critical (missing core spec elements):**\n1. No `Clientset` struct with `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` embedding\n2. No constructors (`NewForConfig`, `NewForConfigAndClient`, `NewForConfigOrDie`, `New`)\n3. No `Discovery()` method on `Interface`\n4. No `RESTClient()` on `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n5. No `DeleteCollection` on either resource interface\n6. No `AgentRuntimeExpansion` / `CodeInterpreterExpansion` interfaces\n7. No `scheme` package with negotiated serializer\n8. No tests for client-go package\n\n**The implementation uses an in-memory `ObjectStore` pattern instead of real REST clients, which deviates fundamentally from the spec's expectation of a standard Kubernetes client-go library.**","time":{"start":1775830137310,"end":1775830137310}}}
